File preview requirements:

- monospaced readable presentation
- line numbers
- horizontal scrolling
- preserve indentation
- recognize common source file extensions
- display large-file warning
- avoid loading extremely large files blindly
- avoid editing files in the first release
- no arbitrary path traversal outside API-exposed locations

Diff viewer requirements:

- unified and split mode if practical
- additions and deletions clearly differentiated
- line numbers
- file summary
- collapse unchanged sections
- accessible labels not dependent solely on color

